  <summary date="2017-05-04T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Highway Restoration Act of 2017

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide for a phaseout of the Mass Transit Account by the end of FY2021. Beginning in FY2022, no funds would be transferred to the account from the Highway Trust Fund.</summary>
